videos.description: Buddy Hield is held to two points in the first half, sinking two free throws with 1:02 minutes remaining.
videos.headline: Hield struggling in the first half

videos.description: Buddy Hield nails a 3-point shot from half court in the final seconds of the Big-12 semifinal, but after review, the shot doesn't count and Oklahoma falls to West Virginia.
videos.headline: Hield's half-court winner not in time

videos.description: Jevon Carter shares how he felt while waiting to hear if Buddy Hield's shot would count and expresses his confidence heading into the Big 12 final against Kansas.
